org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.projects

Class LibraryDependencyGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.projects.LibraryDependencyGraph

  • public class LibraryDependencyGraph
extends Object
    A dependency graph of libraries. Each vertex on the graph represents a library. Each outgoing edge represents a set of classes that cause the "from" vertex to be dependent on the "to" vertex.
